{"tid":1103931,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》北美地區預售票房創紀錄 累積銷售是這4套電影預售總和的2倍","createTime":"2019-04-12T17:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T19:05:54.000Z","uid":66923,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d132cedc51e4d0e6bbb951bea49dfc6656ad0317","tid":1103931,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T17:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMQfM9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMQfM9w.jpg&h=dd681d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ozv3V2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzv3V2R.jpg&h=1b090e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeCeigb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeCeigb.jpg&h=7b94f079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMarvel電影宇宙（MCU）集大成之作《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）預售票在北美地區已經開賣一個禮拜，光是第一天開賣就立刻造成售票系統癱瘓，不難想像這部電影的預售數字會有多驚人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">目前累積的銷售成績就已經是以下4套電影預售加埋的2倍</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）<br />\n2. 《Marvel隊長》（Captain Marvel）<br />\n3. 《水行俠》（Aquaman）<br />\n4. 《星球大戰：最後絕地武士》（Star Wars: The Last Jedi）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjMxNjY2MDU1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY1MTUwNTM@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BMjMxNjY2MDU1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY1MTUwNTM%40._V1_.jpg&h=738389d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ewedit.files.wordpress.com/2019/01/cm_character_1-sht_brie_v3_lg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fewedit.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F01%2Fcm_character_1-sht_brie_v3_lg.jpg&h=385454a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOTk5ODg0OTU5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ3MDY3NjM@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BOTk5ODg0OTU5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDQ3MDY3NjM%40._V1_.jpg&h=0f0c3011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/81Q4JB0yMjL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F81Q4JB0yMjL.jpg&h=af94a4ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這4部電影在北美的預售表現都非常亮眼，殊不知《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》才剛開賣，就輕易達成這4套電影預售成績加起來的總和，且還超越2倍！<br />\n<br />\n目前影史票房排行榜除了《阿凡達》和《鐵達尼號》之外，第3名則為20億6000萬美元的《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars: The Force Awakens），接着才為20億4000萬美元的《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》以及16億美元的《侏儸紀世界》（Jurassic World）。<br />\n<br />\n根據國外的票房預測，《復仇者聯盟4》的北美週末開票成績甚至有可能達到3億美元。畢竟當初《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》就以2億5760萬美元創下開票紀錄，強力主打第三階段最終章並大肆宣傳的《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》，肯定可以輕易超越這個成績。<br />\n<br />\n根據Atom Tickets網站的統計結果，《復仇者聯盟4》預售超越的4部電影，最終在全球創下將近60億美元的票房，其中《Marvel隊長》的票房仍持續成長。光是預售票就達成如此的奇蹟紀錄，也只有Marvel做得到，這也讓人好奇上映後的票房將會有多爆炸性的成績。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.do/ePckv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.do%2FePckv&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8JnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=741c671e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.do/ePckv</a>"},{"pid":"9d75ba1b0f69e000b9149da00d457ebd5c5becd9","tid":1103931,"uid":167658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T19:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAmFYRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAmFYRy.png&h=e0a0a61a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}